     designs, graphical assets, databases, APIs, algorithms, and all associated
     documentation, whether in electronic, printed, or any other form.

1.2  "Owner" means Health-Vision and its successors, assigns, and licensees.

1.3  "Authorized User" means any person or entity that has received express
     written authorization from the Owner to use the Software.

1.4  "Unauthorized Use" means any use, access, reproduction, distribution,
     modification, or exploitation of the Software without prior express
     written consent of the Owner.

